  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A clinical trial of AAV2/5 vector for patients with Defects in RPE65
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A dose escalation and dose expansion (Phase I/II) trial of adults and children with retinal
      dystrophy associated with defects in RPE65. ATIMP will be administered to one eye only in a
      single sub-retinal procedure
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
